@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.06)) * ((v1 + 0.18 / v1 + 0.23) + tmp))
    tmp = 0.23
    v2 = 0.72
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.86)))
    v0 = 0.43
    data[tid] = v0
